The puzzle came from using  and  at
the same time. In fact, without including untwisted sector,  is not reached.
This consideration lead us to define the central charge  for
twisted sector by maximal R-charge of chiral primaries in the twisted sector, 
namely,
c_t:= q_NS ^max  . 
( A side remark: 
If we blindly use  in the spectral flow of the charge, i.e, ,
